\mt1 Esta 
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Estan Ak…®nafarim…®n eghaghaniba, Israelia kantri Persian itir bizir me bativizibar eghaghaniba. Esta uab…® Israelian amizim egha ua Persian kantrin atrivim…®n amuim, o kwin…®n oto. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelian apaniba me m…®sogh me ag…®vasava amima a men akura. 
\ip Dughiar bar ekiar Judaba bar ifongezim, me kamagh a d…®bora ghaze, Purim…®n Dughiar Ekiam. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam Purim…®n Dughiar Ekiar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ki. 
\ip Gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim, ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven dughiatam…®n God…®n ziam bar an osirizir puvat…®. Ez…® n…® eghaghanir kam…®n gan God…®n apangkuvim ko an ifongiamra ganam. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Esta Persian kantrin kwin…®n oto 
\mr (Sapta 1--2) 
\s1 Kwin Vasti atrivim…®n akam batoke 
\p  
\v 1-2 \x - \xo 1:1-2 \xt Esra 4:6\x*Ez…® Atrivim Serksis…®n dughiam…®n, a Persian kantrin atrivim…®n iti, egha uan atrivir dabirabir Susan nguibam…®n itim gapiaghiri, Susa kar Persian nguibar ekiar gavgavim. Serksis 127plan provinsba uaghan dar gari, Indian kantrin ikegha ghua Itiopian kantrin tus.  
\v 3 An atrivim…®n azenir namba 3…®n dughiam, a uan ingangaribar faragha zuir gumaziba ko, gavman…®n gumazir ekiaba isar ekiam bagha men dia. Ez…® Persian kantri ko Midian kantrin m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba ko provinsbar garir gumaziba ko gumazir ekiaba me bar izegha a ko iti. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® isar ekiar kam iak…®nir 6plan iti, ez…® Atrivim Serksis uan dag…®aba ko d…®penim…®n itir bizir aghuiba gumazamizibar akakasi. Ez…® me an bizir bar aghuir ganganir aghuibagh amibar gari. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® iak…®nir 6plan kaba g…®vaz…®ma, atrivim uan d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven a iti nagh…®n isar ekiar igharazim gami. Susan nguibar ekiar gavgavim…®n itir gumaziba bar, biziba itiba ko biziba puvat…®ziba, kar men isam. Me isar kam wan wigh…®n an iti.  
\v 6 Me isam gamua itir danganir bar aghuim, gumaziba fom…®ra dag…®ar agheviba ko ghurghuriba ko bluplaba ko, ongarim…®n itir zoghuaba ko, dag…®ar glas…®n m…®ngariba inigha, nguazim dafegha ghuriar kam…®n ingari. Egha me isam gamir dughiam…®n me danganir kam inir ghurghurim ko p…®ghaghevim ghuaragha benir aghuim…®n a ike. Egha iniba ikezir benir kam, me dag…®ar ak…®nim…®n a guragha, silvan ring…®n aghuibar a g…®tui. Egha me gol…®n dabirabiba ko silvan dabirabiba tintinibar dagheba apir danganir kam…®n ada afe.  
\v 7 Atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba wain isa gol…®n d…®k…®r…®zir kav…®n d…®g…®rir igharagha garibagh inge. Ez…® atrivim uan bizir av…®rim…®n amodogh…®n, wain isa gumazir kabagh an…®gav…®ra iti.  
\v 8 Egha Atrivim Serksis kamagh…®n an d…®penim…®n ingarir gumazibav gei, gumazir wain gifueghav…®ra itiba, wain me dan…®ngv…®ra ik…®. Anogoroziba puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Kwin Vasti isar ekiam, amiziba baghav…®ra, uaghan atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n a gami. 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® isar ekiar kam ikia ghua namba 7…®n aruem…®n otoz…®ma, atrivim wain amegha mong ongani. Egha uan ingarir gumazir 7plan diaz…®ma me a bagha izi. Men ziabar kara: Mehuman ko Bista, Harbona, Bikta, Abakta, Setar ko Karkas.  
\v 11 Atrivim Serksis me amaga me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia mang…® Kwin Vasti inigh iz…®. Kwin Vasti uan kwin…®n dapanir asuam arugh iz…®. Kwin Vastin ganganim bar dera, kamagh…®n k…® a is…® uan nguibabar aven gumazir ekiaba ko, gumazir nan isam…®n izeziba bar men akakaghasa.  
\v 12 Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba ghua Kwin Vasti an m…®g…®r…®g…®abar gun a m…®gei. Ez…® kwin izan aghua. Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n oregha an muriam Kwin Vasti bagha bar mogh…®ra an ikufi. 
\p  
\v 13 Kar atrivim…®n arazim, a fofozir gumazibar azara, kar gumazir faragha zuir dughiabar arazibagh foziba. A men azaraght…®, me gumazibar dabirabim ko arazir aghuiba a m…®k…®mt…®, a fogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a fofozir gumazibar diaz…®ma me ize, egh me a m…®k…®mt…® a man arazitamra kwin damuam.  
\v 14 Ez…® gumazir kaba bar atrivim…®n borogh…®ra ikia, men ziabar kara: Karsena ko Setar, Atmata, Tarsis, Meres, Marsena ko Memukan. 7plan gumazir kaba, me kantri Persia ko kantri Midian gumazir dapaniba, egha gumazir ekiar igharaziba me uaghan me gafira. Ez…® atrivim me baragha men n…®ghn…®zibar g…®rara zui. 
\p  
\v 15 Egha a kamagh…®n 7plan gumazir kabav gei, ‚ÄúK…® Atrivim Serksis, k…® uan ingarir gumaziba Kwin Vasti bagha me amada, ez…® me ghua bizir k…® a damuasa ifongeziba bagha a m…®geima, ez…® a nan akam batoke. Ez…® en arazim manmagh…®n bizir kam m…®gei? E manmagh…®ra kwin damuam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Memukan kamagh atrivim ko an gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim n…® orakigh, Kwin Vasti os…®mt…®zim n…®rarama at…®zir puvat…®. An os…®mt…®ziba isa bar n…®n gumazir dapaniba ko n…® garir provinsbar gumazibagh ar…®ki.  
\v 17 Guizbang…®ra, n…® garir nguibabar aven itir amiziba, me bar kwin…®n arazir kurar kam baragham. Egh amiziba kamagh m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòAtrivim Serksis Kwin Vasti m…®g…®a ghaze amang an ganam, ez…® kwin aghuagha atrivim…®n akam batoke.‚Äô Amiziba uaghan akaba batogh uan pabar akaba baraghan kogham.  
\v 18 Dughiar kamra Persian ko Midian gumazir dapanibar amuiba kwin amizir arazir kam baregh, egh uan paba arazir kamra an gun me m…®k…®mam, egh amiziba akar kurabav k…®m…®va arazir kurar av…®ribar amuam. 
\p  
\v 19 ‚ÄúEz…® atrivim, n…® akar k…® m…®geim gifuegh…®va, n…® akam gumazamiziba bagh anemadagh kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòVasti ua iz…® Atrivim Serksis…®n ganan kogham.‚Äô N…® ak…®nafarir Persia ko Midian araziba aven itim, n…® a inigh arazir kam osirigh. Eght…® arazir kam ik…® kamagh…®ra ikiam. Egh n…® amizir aghuir igharazitam inight…®, a Kwin Vastin danganim inigh kwin…®n ik…®.  
\v 20 Eght…® n…®n akam nguibar n…® gariba bar dar mang…®ght…®, amiziba bar uan pabar akaba baragh men apengan ikiam, gumazir ziaba itiba ko ziaba puvat…®ziba uaghara.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® atrivim uan gumazir dapaniba ko me m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gifonge, kamagh…®n atrivim Memukan m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami.  
\v 22 Egha atrivim ak…®nafarim provins…®n a gariba bagha anemada, egha gumazamiziba m…®geir men nguibam…®n akabar me osiri mogh…®ra me bagha ada osirigha, kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazimra uan d…®penim…®n itir darazir ko biziba bar dar dapanim…®n ikiam.‚Äù\f + \fr 1:22 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar otevir kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir pu. Gumazir maba akar kam g…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazimra uan amuiroghboribar dapanim, egh a uan danganim…®n m…®k…®mam.‚Äù\f* 
\c 2  
\s1 Esta kwin…®n oto 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®ma, Atrivim Serksis…®n adarim am…®raz…®ma, a ua Vasti gamizir arazim gin…®r…®, a Kwin Vasti ag…®vaght…® a ua kwin…®n ikian kogham.  
\v 2 Ez…® gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba a gan…®diba a koma apiagha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ti ua bagh amizir igiar igharazitaba buriam. Me ganganir aghuiba ik…® egh uaghan araziba deragh.  
\v 3 Egh n…® uan provins…®n n…® ativagha garibar gumazitaba m…®seveght…®, me amizir igiar aghuiba inigh gavman…®n nguibar ekiar gavgavim Susan iz…®, egh me is…® d…®penir n…® amiziba akuvi nagh…®n me ar…®kigh. Eght…® Hegai, gumazir n…®n amizibar garim,\f + \fr 2:3 \ft Hegai atrivim…®n amuibar ganamin ingangarim iti. Ez…® Serkis…®n atrivir dughiam…®n, atriviba amuir av…®ribar ikia egha amuir doziba sara iti. Atriviba uan amuir doziba isa d…®penibar da ar…®zi, ingangarir gumazir maba men gari. Me ingangarir gumazir kaba men amuiba ko daku me gikararangan me atiatigha men turiar ov…®ziba bar dar ghore.\f* a deragh men ganam. Eght…® amiziba borem uan m…®karzibar aghu egh uari as…®ng…®va, ganganir aghuibar amuam.  
\v 4 Eght…® n…® amizir kabar tav gifongegh, egh tav am…®seveght…® a Kwin Vastin danganim iniam.‚Äù Atrivim oregha bar akar kam gifonge, egha kamagh…®n damuasa. 
\p  
\v 5 Dughiar kam Susan nguibar ekiar gavgavim…®n aven Judan gumazir mam iti, an ziam Mordekai. Mordekain afeziam…®n ziam, Jair. Jair a Simein ovavir borir mam, Kis…®n otarim. Mordekai, a Benjamin…®n adarazir mav.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt 2 Atriviba 24:10-16; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10\x*Ez…® faragha Babilon…®n Atrivim Nebukatnesar, Judan Atrivim Jehoiakim ko Judan marazi iniz…® me ghua Babilon…®n kalabus…®n ike. Egha Mordekai iniz…® a me ko uaghan ghu.  
\v 7 Mordekai guivir mam iti, an ziam Esta, ez…® guiz…®n Hibrun akam…®n an ziam Hadasa, ez…® Esta Mordekain afeziar dozim…®n guivim. Ez…® an afeziar dozim uan amuim ko aning areme, ez…® Mordekai Esta inigha uan borim…®n m…®raram a gami. Ez…® Esta bar deragha ganganir aghuim gami. 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Atrivim Serksis gumaziba ko amiziba bagha akam amaga ghaze, me amizir igiar av…®riba inigh Susan nguibam…®n iz…®. Ez…® me amizir igiaba inigha iza uaghan Esta inigha ize. Me Esta isa atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n amiziba itir danganim…®n anet…®. Ez…® Hegai amizibagh ativagha men gari.  
\v 9 Hegai Estan garima a bar deraz…®ma a bar a gifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a m…®karziba adir borem ko dagher bar aghuiba Esta gan…®ngi. Egha amiziba itir d…®penim…®n danganir faraghav…®ra itim, an a isa Esta gan…®ngi. Egha atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n 7plan amizir igiaba am…®sevez…®ma, me Esta ko ikia deragha a gami. 
\p  
\v 10 Mordekai faragha Esta m…®g…®a ghaze, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n mang…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, a Judan amizim.  
\v 11 Dughiaba bar Mordekai amiziba itir d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akam garuav…®ra iti. A Estan ik…®r…®m…®rim g…®foghasa a manmagh…®ram amua iti. Egha a uaghan foghasa bizir tizimra Esta bativam. 
\p  
\v 12 Azenir vam…®ran aven, me amizibar m…®karziba ak…®raghasez…®ma men ganganiba bar dera. Iak…®nir 6plan me mean temem…®n apongezir borem…®n amizibar m…®karziba aghefi. Egha iak…®nir 6plan igharazibar me borer mughuriar aghuim zuim…®n me aghefi. Bizir kabar g…®n me guivir igiaba vaghvagha me isa ghua Atrivim Serksis…®n akakasi.  
\v 13 Egh dughiar amizim atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n mangasava amim, uab…® ifongez…® mogh…®n uab…® as…®ngigh atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n mang…®.  
\v 14 Amizir atrivim bagha zuim, a guarat…®zim…®n ik…® mang…®t…® am…®nim dutugham. Eght…® am…®mzaraghan me a inigh mang…® amizibar d…®penir igharazim…®n Sasgas…®n dafarim dat…®gham. Sasgas, an atrivim…®n amuir dozibar d…®penim…®n garir gumazim. Amuir kam uam atrivim bagh mangan kogham. Atrivim a gifuegh…®va an ziam d…®borogh an diaght…®ma a mangam. Tuaviba ua puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Esta mang…® atrivim…®n ganamin dughiam oto. Esta Abihail…®n guivim, Abihail a Mordekain afeziar dozim. Mordekai ua bagha Esta inigha uan borim…®n m…®rarama a gami. Gumaziba bar Estan gara bar a gifonge. Esta ghua atrivim…®n garir dughiam…®n a uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua uab…® as…®ngizir pu, puvat…®. An amizibar garir gumazim Hegai, a m…®kemez…® korotiabaram aghui.  
\v 16 Ez…® dughiar kam Serksis atrivim…®n iti 7plan azeniba. Azenir kam…®n iak…®nir namba 10 me a d…®bora ghaze Tebet, me an Esta inigha atrivim bagha zui.\f + \fr 2:16 \ft Iak…®nim Tebet, a en namba 10…®n iak…®nim Oktoban m…®n iti.\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® atrivim amizir igharazibar aghuagha Esta bar a gifonge. A Estan garima an amizir igharaziba bar me gafiragha, an ganganiba bar dera. Amizir igiar igharaziba Estan m…®n atrivim…®n d…®ghorim kuarizir pu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim kwin…®n dapanir asuam an dapanim garu. Ez…® Esta Kwin Vastin danganim inigha kwin…®n oto.  
\v 18 Egha Atrivim Serksis Esta kwin…®n otozir bizim bagha isar ekiam d…®boro. Egha uan gumazir dapaniba ko ingangarir gumazir dapanibar dia, eght…® me isar ekiar kam bagh izam. A ghaze, ‚ÄúNan kantrin itir gumazamiziba dughiar kam…®n avughsam.‚Äù Egha atrivim uan bizir av…®ribar amodogh…®n, bizir aghuir av…®riba isa gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. 
\s1 Mordekai atrivim…®n akuraz…®ma an os…®mt…®zim inizir pu 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® dughiar kam me amizir igiaba ua me akufa. Ez…® dughiar kamra,\f + \fr 2:19 \ft Hibrun akam vez…®n kam…®n m…®ngarim derav…®ra bigha m…®geir puvat…®.\f* atrivim Mordekai am…®sevez…®ma an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gumazir dapanir mam…®n iti.  
\v 20 Mordekai faragha kamagh…®n Esta m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® gumazitam m…®k…®man mark…®, egh suam, n…® Judabar amizim. Ez…® Esta an akam…®n m…®rara ghu, egha Mordekain akaba baragha dar g…®n zui, kar a zurarama amir arazim. 
\p  
\v 21 Mordekai, Atrivim Serksis…®n ingangarim gamir dughiam…®n, gumazir pumuning adarim atrivim…®n ikia a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa akam m…®soke. Aning…®n ziamning, Biktana ko Teres. Gumazir kamning atrivim itir danganim…®n tiar akam…®n garir ingangarim gami.  
\v 22 Ez…® Mordekai aning…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha ghua Kwin Esta m…®keme. Ez…® Esta kamagh…®n oregha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam isa atrivim gan…®ngigha, ghaze, kar Mordekain akurvazim n…® bagha izi. Ez…® atrivim fo, Mordekai akar kam baraki.  
\v 23 Me akar aning m…®kemezim…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghasa amuv…®ra ikia, egha a g…®fo a guizbang…®ra. Egha me temem…®n aning aguraz…®ma aning areme. Egha atrivim kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBizir otozir kam, e uan gavman…®n ak…®nafarim…®n aven eghaghanim…®n m…®n an osirigh.‚Äù Ez…® me atrivim…®n damazim…®n a m…®kemez…® mogh…®rama ami. 
\c 3  
\ms1 Haman Judabagh as…®ghas…®ghasa 
\mr (Sapta 3--5) 
\s1 Haman Judaba kuvar…®masa akam m…®soke 
\p  
\v 1 Egha g…®n Atrivim Serksis gavman…®n faragh mangasa gumazir mam am…®sefe, an ziam Haman, Haman a Hamedatan otarim, egha Agak…®n adarazir mav.  
\v 2 Egha atrivim ingangaribar faragha zuir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, me Haman bagh teviba ap…®r…®va an ziam fam. Me bar mogh…®ra atrivim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami, ez…® Mordekai uab…®ra puvat…®. Mordekai bar mogh…®ra Haman bagh teviba ap…®ran aghua. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangaribar faragha zuir gumazir igharaziba ganigha kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha atrivim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®n mangan aghua?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Dughiar av…®ribar me Mordekain arazir kam bagha a m…®gei, ez…® Mordekai men akaba baraghan aghua. Mordekai kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Judan adarazir gumazir mam, kamagh…®n k…® Haman bagh uan tevimning ap…®righan kogham.‚Äù\f + \fr 3:4 \ft Haman, a Agak…®n adarazir mav, Agak, a Amalekian gumazim. Ez…® Amalekia me Judabar apanim gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Mordekai a bagh tevimning ap…®ran aghua. N…® Ua Me Ini 17:8-16 ko God…®n Araziba 25:17-19…®n gan.\f* Ez…® ingangaribar faragha zuir gumaziba Mordekain m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n gun Haman m…®keme. Kamagh…®n me gan foghasa, Haman ti Mordekai ateght…® a kamagh…®ra damuam, o puvat…®gham. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Haman gari Mordekai a bagha teviba ap…®ri puvat…®gha an ziam feir puvat…®, ez…® an a bagha an muriam bar an ikufi.  
\v 6 Haman g…®n kamagh…®n fo, Mordekai a Judabar mav, kamagh…®n a Mordekai gas…®ghas…®ghasa akam m…®soke. Mordekai uab…®ra puvat…®. Haman tuavitam g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh Judan Persian kantrin itir darazi bar mogh…®ra me m…®sueght…® me arighireghasa n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 7 Dughiar kam Serksis atrivim…®n itima an namba 12 azenir kam…®n iak…®nir farazim Nisan, Haman ghaze, me satu gikararang egh iak…®nim ko dughiar aghuir Judabagh as…®ghas…®ghamim g…®fogham. Me ikararegha g…®vagha kamagh…®n fo, namba 12 iak…®nim Adar,\f + \fr 3:7 \ft Iak…®nim Nisan, a en iak…®nimning Mas ko Epril…®n m…®n iti. Ez…® Adar…®n iak…®nim a en iak…®nimning Februari ko Mas…®n m…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Haman damuasa m…®geir bizim bagh m…®zuam mang…®t…® namba 11 iak…®nim otoght…® an a damuam.\f* an dughiar namba 13…®n, Haman Judabagh as…®ghas…®gham. 
\p  
\v 8 Egha Haman ghua kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizir igharazibar marazi n…®n kantrin nguibaba tintinibar dar aven iti. Egha kagh iti darazi amir araziba me ko dagh amir puvat…®. Me bar ighara, egha atrivim…®n arazibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n n…® me ateght…® me ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, bizir kam n…®n akuraghan koght…®, n…®n kantri deragh mangan kogham.  
\v 9 Ore atrivim, n…® ifuegh akam gumazamiziba bagh anemadaght…®, me bar gumazamizir kabav sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh. K…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® ifuegh…®va akam gumazamiziba bagh anemadaght…®, me gumazamizir kabav sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh. K…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, n…® kamagh…®n damight…® k…® 10 tausen silvan dag…®aba is…® n…®n dag…®ar d…®penim dat…®gham, eght…® me dag…®ar kabar atrivim…®n ingangarir kam damuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Atrivim Serksis dafarim gazuir ring…®n mam iti, ring…®n kam atrivim…®n ziam ko nedazim an ikia egha an arazir an amiba gavgavim dagh an…®di. Ez…® atrivim m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha ring…®n kam suegha Judabar apanim gamir gumazim Haman gan…®ngi.  
\v 11 Egha atrivim a m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® ifonge dag…®aba ateght…® da ik…®. Bizir tizim n…® gumazamizir kabar amus…®, a dera n…® puram a damu. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® iak…®nir faragha zuim…®n dughiar namba 13…®n, Haman gumazir atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osiribar diaz…®ma me izi. Ez…® a uan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba bar me m…®kemez…® me a m…®kemez…® biziba bar ada osiri. Me Atrivim Serksis garir nguibar kaba, me bar me bagha men nguibabar akabar me osirir arazim…®n m…®n da osiri. An ak…®nafariba gumazir dapanir ekiaba ko provinsbar garir gumazir dapaniba ko nguibabar garir gumazir ekiaba bagha da osiri. Ez…® ak…®nafariba bar Atrivim Serksis dafarim gazuir ring…®n ababanim dar iti. Ring…®n ababanir kam kamagh…®n akagha ghaze, atrivim uab…® ak…®nafarir kaba osiri.  
\v 13 Ez…® gumazir ak…®nafarir kaba inigh mangamiba, me d…®kavigha atrivim garir nguibar kaba bar adar ghu. Ak…®nafarir kaba bar kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAdar…®n iak…®nim…®n namba 13…®n dughiam…®n ia Judan adarazi bar me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghiregh. Gumazir igiaba ko, gumazir ghuriba ko, amiziba ko, boriba dughiar kamra bar me kuavaremegh, egh men apangkuvan mark…®. Dughiar kamra bar me kuavaremegh egh bar men biziba inigh.  
\v 14 Eght…® gumazir dapaniba provinsba bar dar aven itir gumazamiziba bagh ak…®nafarir kam d…®pont…®, me bar mogh…®rama a baragh. Eght…® dughiar kam otivt…®, me magh…®rama Judabav soght…® me ar…®mighiram.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® gumazir ak…®nafarir kam inigha zuiba, me zuam…®ra ghua kantrin kam…®n nguibaba bar a adagh arui. Egha me Susan nguibar ekiam…®n uaghan ak…®nafarim…®n akam akuni, ez…® gumaziba bar oraki. Ez…® atrivim ko Haman, uaningra ikia wain apava uaning m…®g…®ava eghari. Ez…® Susan itir gumazamiziba m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha d…®gavir kuram gamigha n…®ghn…®ghava avenge. 
\c 4  
\s1 Mordekai uab…®n akurvaghasa Estan azangs…®si 
\p  
\v 1 Mordekai kamagh…®n oregha bar atiatingi. Kamagh…®n a uan korotiaba abigha bar oseme. Egha azirakar korotiar b…®b…®ziba aghuigha averenim isa uan dapanir ar…®zim gaghui, egha tuavir kam…®n men akaghasa, a bar oseme. Egha a nguibar ekiam…®n aven arua pamten azirakar ighiabagh ami.  
\v 2 A ghua atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akamra tu, egha aven ghuzir puvat…®. A fo, gumazim aven mang…®s…®, azirakar korotiar b…®b…®ziba aghuigh, aven mangan kogham.  
\v 3 Ez…® dughiar kam atrivim…®n ak…®nafarim kantrin kam…®n provinsba bar a dar ghuz…® me oraki, ez…® Judan gumazamizibar naviba bar osemez…® me pamten diava arava azir ighiabagh ami. Me arava daghetam apir puvat…®. Egha Judan gumazamizir av…®riba azirakar korotiar b…®b…®ziba aghuigha averenim gakui. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Estan ingangarir amiziba ko an garir gumaziba a bagha ghua Mordekai amir arazibar gun a m…®gei. Ez…® Kwin Esta d…®gavir kuram gamigha osemegha n…®ghn…®ghava avenge. Egha a korotiar maba Mordekai bagha da amaga danganir uari akuvim…®n ghaze, an azirakar korotiar maba suegh egh korotiar aghuir kabar aghuigh. Ez…® Mordekai ada inian aghua.  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n Esta Hatak…®n diaz…® an a bagha izi. Hatak ana amizibar garir gumazir mam, atrivim faragha Hatak am…®sevegha ghaze, a Estan ingangarim damuam. Hatak izez…®ma, Esta anemaga ghaze, n…® mang…® nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n Mordekai batogh. Egh an azaragh deragh fogh, a manmaghsua arazir kabagh ami? 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Hatak nguibar ekiam…®n tong…®n atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n ghua Mordekai bato.  
\v 7 Ez…® Mordekai bizir Haman m…®kemeziba ko a gamiziba ko, Judaba ovengeght…®, dag…®ar Haman m…®kemezir mogh…®ra gavman…®n d…®penim dat…®ghamba, bar dar gun Hatak m…®keme.  
\v 8 Egha ak…®nafarir me Susan nguibar ekiam…®n osirigha provinsba bar dar amadaziba, Mordekai dar mam inigha Hatak gan…®ngi. Ak…®nafarir kam Judan gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghamin m…®g…®r…®g…®aba an iti. Egha Mordekai a m…®g…®a ghaze, ak…®nafarim…®n m…®ngarim Esta gegharagh a m…®kemegh. Hatak Esta m…®kemeght…® a mang…® uan gumazamiziba bagh atrivim gaghon…®va kamagh…®n an azaragham, a Estan adarazir apangkuvight…® me ovengan kogham. 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Hatak uamategha ghua bizir Mordekai a m…®kemeziba, bar adar gun Esta m…®keme.  
\v 10 Ez…® Esta Mordekai bagha m…®g…®r…®g…®am uam Hatak gan…®ngiz…® an a inigha ghua Mordekai gan…®ngi.  
\v 11 A ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n iti, gumazamiziba bar a g…®fo. A ghaze, n…® tina pura uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n atrivim…®n gans…®, tiar akar aven itim…®n mang…®ghan kogham. Bar puvat…®. N…® kamagh…®n damigh n…® ovegham. A uab…® n…®n diaght…® n…® mang…®va an ganam. Tuavir vam…®ra kamagh iti, n…® aven mang…®t…® atrivim n…®n ganigh uan gol…®n atrivir fidizim feght…®, n…® oveghan kogham. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, atrivim nan diaz…® k…® an ganasa aven ghuzir puvat…®z…® iak…®nir vam…®ra g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Mordekai Estan m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha,  
\v 13 a ikaragha n…®ghn…®zim a gan…®ga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ghaze, n…® atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n iti, egha ghaze n…® deraghv…®ra ikiam. N…® Judaba en m…®n uaghan m…®zazim iniam.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Jon 12:27\x*N…® aghumra kamagh…®n uab…®n asugh ik…®t…®ma, akurvazir igharazim p…®n ikegh izighir…® Judan adarazir akuraght…® me os…®mt…®zir kam gitagham.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Estan ak…®nafarim…®n aven me God…®n ziam d…®borozir puvat…®, ez…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam, ‚Äúakurvazir igharazim p…®n ikegh izighir…® Judan adarazir akuraght…® me os…®mt…®zir kam gitagham,‚Äù an akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®n iti. A kamagh m…®k…®masa, ‚ÄúGod tuavir igharazitam batoght…® a en akuragham.‚Äù\f* N…® oveght…® n…®n afeziam…®n adarazi uaghan g…®vagham. Eght…® tina fogham? N…® ti tizim bagha kantrin kam…®n kwin…®n oto? N…® kwin…®n otozir bizir kam, ka ti dughiar aghuir n…®n adarazi os…®mt…®zim…®n iti, ez…® kar men akurvaghamin dughiar aghuim.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Esta a bagha kamagh…®n akam uam anemada,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Judan Susan nguibam…®n itiba bar me inigh me akuvagh, egh kamagh…®n damu. Ia aruer 3pla ko d…®magarir 3plan dagheba, atagh…®ragh na bagh n…®ghn…®gh. Eght…® k…® uan ingangarir amiziba ko e uaghan kamagh…®ra damuam. Eght…® bizir kam…®n g…®n, k…® atrivim bagh mangam. E fo, k…® mangamin arazir kam, kar k…® atrivim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim ab…®gham. Egh k…® kamagh…®n damigh ovengs…® ovegham, akaba pu, a dera.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Mordekai atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akam ategh ghua Esta a m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra a biziba bar dagh ami. 
\c 5  
\s1 Esta, atrivim ko Haman isar ekiam bagh mangasa, atrivim…®n azangs…®si 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Esta 3plan dughiabar dagheba ta. Egha bizir kam…®n g…®n a uan kwin…®n korotiaba aghuigha ghua atrivim iti nagh…®n d…®vazim…®n borogh…®n tughav ikia, atrivim apiaghiri nagh…®n gari. Kar atrivim itir danganir ekiam. Ez…® atrivim uan dabirabim gaperaghav ikia tiar akam…®n azenan gari.  
\v 2 Egha a gari, Kwin Esta azenan tughav ikia egha atrivim…®n n…®ghn…®zim gekuigha uab…® m…®k…®ni, ez…® a bar a gifonge. Egha atrivim uan gol…®n atrivir fidizim Estan akuigha anemadaz…®ma, Esta izava an ruaghatevim…®n suira. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKwin Esta, manmagh…®n amiz…® n…® na bagha izi? N…® bizitam gifuegh na bagh iz…® egh na m…®k…®m, eght…® k…®, ativagha garir nguibam…®n biziba, k…® tong…®ra da abigh…®va egh akuatam n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® Esta an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, dat…®r…®gh…®n d…®mangan k…® isar mam n…® bagh a damuam. Eght…® n…® ifuegh…®va, n…® ko Haman isar ekiar kam bagh izasa k…® n…®n azangs…®si.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® atrivim akar kam gifuegha, Haman bagha akam amaga ghaze, a zuam…®ra izegh…®va aning Estan isam…®n mang…®va an azangs…®zir bizim damuam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim Haman ko Estan isam bagha ghu. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha isam…®n me wain apa ghua, atrivim ua Estan azara, ‚ÄúKwin Esta, bizir n…® ifuegha na m…®k…®masava amim, na m…®k…®m. Eght…® nguibar k…® ativagha garim k…® tong…®ra anebigh egh akuatam n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Esta a ikaragha ghaze,  
\v 8 ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® ti n…®n damazim…®n deraz…® n…® na gifonge, egh n…® nan azangs…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®s…® ifongeght…®, Atrivim k…® uam n…®n azangs…®si, k…® gurumzaraghan isar igharazim n…® ko Haman bagh uam a damuam. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, gua gurumzaraghan isar kam…®n ua izam. Dughiar kam…®n bizir k…® ifongegha n…® m…®k…®masava amim, k…® n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\s1 Haman Mordekai m…®sueght…®  // an aremeghasa tuavim ak…®ri 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Haman dughiar kam…®n dagher danganim ategha bar akuegha navir am…®rizim…®n zui. Egha a ghua Mordekain garima an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven zuir d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n m…®n aperaghav iti. Egha tong d…®kavigha Haman gifuegha dughiam a gan…®dir puvat…®. A tong an atiatir puvat…®. An ganganir kam Haman gamiz…® an n…®ghn…®zim ikuviz…® a bar a basemegha puv…®ram atari.  
\v 10 Egha Haman pura uan os…®mt…®zim ab…®ragha uan d…®penim…®n ghu. Egha uan namakabar diaz…® me izi, ez…® a uaghan uan amuim Seres m…®kemez…®ma a uaghan me ko iti. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® me otivigha g…®vaz…®ma Haman men damazim…®n uab…®ra uan ziam fe. Egha me m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® dag…®ar av…®riba ko, bizir av…®riba ko, borir av…®riba iti. Egha ghaze, atrivim na isa p…®n na at…®gha ingangarir ekiam na gan…®ngi. Ez…® ingangarir gumazir igharaziba bar nan apengan iti. 
\p  
\v 12 Egha Haman ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKwin Esta, uab…® isar ekiar mam gamigha gumazir igharazitam…®n diazir puvat…®. An atrivim ko narara inabaz…®ma ga ghu. Egha ghaze, guarara gurumzaraghan mang…® a ko ua damam.  
\v 13 Egha k…® Judabar adarazir gumazim Mordekain garima, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n aperaghav iti. Ez…® nan muriam a bagha bar ikufi. Ez…® k…® n…®ghn…®zi, bizir aghuir k…® m…®kemez…® kaba pura biziba.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Haman…®n amuim Seres ko, an namakaba n…®ghn…®zir mam batogha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® n…®ghn…®gh os…®man mark…®. N…® gumazibav kemeght…®, me temer ruaritam asaragh, eght…® an ruarim 20 mitan tugh. Eght…® n…® gurum bar m…®zaraghara mang…® atrivim m…®kemegh egh Mordekai inigh an f…®rim dafagh an eguraght…® an aremegh. N…® kamagh…®n damigh, navir am…®rizim inigh mang…® damam.‚Äù Haman m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gifuegha gumazibav kemez…®, me Mordekai guasa temer mam asara. 
\c 6  
\ms1 Judaba derav…®ra ikiamin  // tuavim bato 
\mr (Sapta 6--10) 
\s1 Atrivim ziar ekiam isa Mordekai gan…®ngi 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® d…®magarir kamra atrivim derav…®rama akuizir puvat…®. Egha ak…®nafarim…®n aven eghaghanir bizir an kantrin otiviz…® me osiriziba bagha me m…®gei, eght…® me da inigh iz…® a bagh dar ponam.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Esta 2:21-22\x*Egha me Biktana ko Teres…®n eghaghanim d…®bori, aning atrivim…®n danganir a itim…®n garir gumazimning. Gumazir kamning atrivim m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuavir mam bato. Ez…® g…®n Mordekai aning…®n n…®ghn…®zim g…®fogha aning…®n gun m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE bizir aghuir manamra Mordekai amizir ingangarir kam bagha a ikara?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® gumaziba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúE bizitam guizbang…®ra a gan…®ngizir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúNan ingangarir gumazitaba d…®penir kam…®n iti, o puvat…®?‚Äù Ez…® bar dat…®r…®gh…®ra Haman atrivim…®n d…®penir tiar akam…®n azenan tughav iti. An atrivim…®n azaragh egh mang…® Mordekai temer a kuazazim…®n an f…®rim dafagh a guasa. Kamagh…®n Haman uab…® atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven izi. 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba an ganigha kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúHaman izegha g…®vagha n…® m…®zua kagh iti. A n…®n ganasa.‚Äù Ez…® atrivim ghaze, a inigh aven iz…®. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Haman aven izima atrivim a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir mam iti, ez…® k…® ziar ekiam a dan…®ngasa. Egha k…® fozir pu, k…® bizir aghuir manatam a dan…®ngam. Ez…® n…®n n…®ghn…®zim, k…® manmagh…®ram a damuam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Haman uab…®ra uab…® g…®n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim tinara bizir aghuir kam…®n a damuam? Ua gumaziba puvat…®, kar k…®rara.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7-8 Egha Haman kamagh…®n atrivim…®n akam ikara, ‚ÄúN…® m…®k…®mt…®, me korotiar n…® uab…® azuim inigh mang…® gumazir kam darugh. Egh n…® uan hoziar mam inigh, atrivim…®n dapanir asuam is…® hoziam…®n dapanim uaghan anes…®ngigh.  
\v 9 Egh n…® uan ingangarir gumazir faragh zuitam a m…®seveght…®, a gumazir kam n…®n korotiam…®n anes…®ngam. Eght…® gumazir kam hoziam daperaght…®, n…®n ingangarir gumazir kam a inigh nguibar ekiam…®n danganir uari akuvim…®n mang…®. Egh aning mangamin dughiam ingangarir gumazim kamagh…®n d…®m m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIa bar gumazir kam…®n gan. Atrivim ziar ekiam a gan…®ngi. Egh arazir aghuir atrivim a gamim…®n gan!‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® atrivim akar kam baregha Haman m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúBar dera! N…® zuam…®ra mang…® korotiam ko hoziam inigh, egh ziar ekiam Judabar gumazim Mordekai dan…®ngigh, a gumazir nan d…®penir tiar akam…®n ingarim. Egh bizir n…® m…®kemeziba, n…® bar dar amigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Haman atrivim…®n korotiam inigha iza Mordekai garu. Ez…® Mordekai hoziam gaperaz…® Haman a inigha ghua nguibar ekiam…®n uari akuvi nagh…®n ghu. Aning ghuav…®ra ikia Haman kamagh…®n gumazibar d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa bar gumazir kam…®n gan. Atrivim ziar ekiam a gan…®ngi. Egh arazir aghuir atrivim a gamim…®n gan!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Aning kamagh…®n amigha g…®vagha, g…®n Mordekai uamategha atrivim…®n ingangarim bagha ghu. Ez…® Haman bar aghums…®gha navim bar a basemez…®, a uan guam avaragha ara uan d…®penim…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 13 Egha a uan amuim ko namakaba bizir a bativizibar gun bar me m…®keme. An amuim ko an namakar fofozir av…®riba itiba, me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n n…®n ziam ko gavgavim Mordekai n…® dama a iniasa. A Judan gumazim, n…® aneb…®ns…® damuva avegham. A n…® d…®kab…®ragh n…® ag…®vagham. Eght…® n…® puram an guraghav ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Esta Haman…®n gun atrivim m…®gei 
\p  
\v 14 Egha me uariv g…®av…®ra itima, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven ingarir gumaziba otifi. Egh Haman inigh Estan isam bagh zuam…®ra mangasa. 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1-2 Ez…® kar namba 2…®n dughiam atrivim ko Haman ghugha Esta koma api. Me wain apa egha daghem…®n tong…®n atrivim uam Estan azara, ‚ÄúKwin Esta, bizir n…® ifuegha na m…®k…®masava amim, n…® na m…®k…®m. Eght…®, nguibar k…® ativagha garim, k…® tong…®ra anebigh egh akuatam n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Esta a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® n…®n azangs…®si, n…®n ifongiam nan azangs…®zim…®n ik…®t…®, n…® nan azangs…®zim ikaragh. Ez…® nan azangs…®zimra kara, k…® ko nan adarasi, e ovengan k…® aghua. E angam…®ra ikiasa.  
\v 4 K…® kamagh…®n oraki, gumazir mam k…® uan adarazi ko e m…®sueght…® e aremeghamin tuavim at…®gha g…®fa. Me bar e kuavaremeghasa. Egh me k…® uan adarazi ko e is…®, pura kalabuziar amiziba ko gumazibar m…®n ik…®s…®, e iniam, eght…® k…® n…® m…®k…®mamin akaba puvat…®gham. K…® os…®mt…®zim n…® dan…®ngan aghua. Ez…® me bar e kuvar…®masa, kamagh…®n k…® bizir kam…®n gun m…®gei.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Ez…® Atrivim Serksis kamagh…®n oregha Estan azara, ‚ÄúTina atiatiba puvat…®gha, n…® m…®geir bizir kabar amut…® da otivasa. Ez…® gumazir kam managh iti?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Esta a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Haman m…®gei. A en apanim damu egh e gas…®ghas…®ghasa.‚Äù Ez…® Haman, Atrivim Serksis ko Kwin Esta, aning…®n guamning…®n bar aguaghfagha bar atiatingi.  
\v 7 Ez…® atrivim puv…®ra atara d…®kavigha pura dagher dakozim ategha azenan ghua uan d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven itir plauan azenim…®n ghu. Guizbang…®ra Haman…®n ganganim, atrivim bizir kam bagh os…®mt…®zim a dan…®ngam. A ua bagh Kwin Esta m…®k…®m…®va a gaghorasa. A ghaze, an apangkuvim nan ik…®, egh atrivim na bagh m…®k…®mt…®, a na gas…®ghas…®ghan kogham. Kamagh…®n a d…®penim…®n aven ikiav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 8 Egha a bar osemegha dakozir Esta aperaghav itim…®n uab…® ekunigha uab…®n akurvaghasa Esta gaghori. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®ra atrivim azenim…®n ikegha aven iza kamagh…®n ganigha, pamten tuaragha m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazir kam ti nan d…®penim…®n nan damazim…®n arazir kurabar kwin damuasa?‚Äù 
\p Atrivim m…®kemez…®, an ingangarir gumaziba magh…®ra iza, Haman…®n guam avara, arazir kam…®n me gumaziba bar men akaghasa, atrivim Haman m…®sueght…® an aremegham.  
\v 9 Ez…® atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ingangarir gumazir mam an ziam Harbona, a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúHaman temer ak…®nir mam uan d…®penim…®n borogh…®n anesara. Ez…® an ruarim 20 mitan tu. A Mordekai dafagh aneguasa ingarizir bizim, gumazir fom…®ra atrivim…®n akuraz…®ma an ovengezir puvat…®zim.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® atrivim akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mang…® Haman is…® temer ak…®nir kam…®n an f…®rim dafagh aneguraght…®, an aremegh.‚Äù  
\v 10 Ez…® me Haman inigha, a Mordekai aguasa asarazir tememram Haman agura. Me kamagh…®n amigha g…®vaz…®ma atrivim navir am…®rizim isi. 
\c 8  
\s1 Atrivim Judabav g…®a ghaze, me uan apanibar m…®doroziba ikarvagham 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Judabar apanim Haman ovengezir dughiamra, Atrivim Serksis an d…®penim ko an biziba bar ada isa Kwin Esta gan…®ngi. Ez…® Esta atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, Mordekai na ko e ik…®zir vam…®ra, a kamagh…®n atrivim m…®kemez…® Mordekai iza atrivim…®n guam…®n tu.  
\v 2 Ez…® atrivim uan dafarim…®n ring suegha a isa Mordekai gan…®ngi. Ring…®n kam atrivim…®n ziam…®n ababanim an iti. Ring…®n kamra Haman faragha uan dafarim gar…®si, ez…® atrivim a inigha, Mordekai gan…®ngi. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Esta Mordekai a m…®sevez…®ma, a Haman…®n d…®penim ko an biziba bar dagh ativagha dar gari. 
\p  
\v 3 Egha g…®n Esta atrivim bagha ua ghugha, an dagarimning…®n borogh…®n ir…®, egha azia temeriba ira iti. Egha a gumazir arazir kurar kam gamiziba bagha atrivim…®n azangs…®si, eght…® an apangkuvim ik…® me m…®kemeght…® me uam arazir kurar Haman Judabar amuasa m…®kemezim damuan kogham.  
\v 4 Ez…® atrivim uan gol…®n atrivir fidizim isa Estan amadaz…®ma, a d…®kavigha ghaze,  
\v 5 ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® ua n…®n azangs…®si, n…®n ifongiam nan azangs…®zim…®n ik…®, egh n…® na gifongegh, egh n…® nan akam gifongeght…®, k…® n…®n damazim…®n deragham, kamagh…®n n…® nan azangs…®zim ikaragh. Egh ak…®nafarir gavgavitam osirigh egh uan nguibar ekiaba bagh ada amadagh. Eght…® me fogham, Haman a Agak…®n adarazir mav, a Hamedatan otarim, a Judabagh as…®ghas…®ghamin n…®ghn…®zir kam me anetegh a damuan mark…®.  
\v 6 Os…®mt…®zir kam nan adarazi bativan k…® bar aghua. Egh me nan adarazi bar me gas…®ghasight…®, nan dabirabim manmagh…®n deragh ik…®v…®ra ikiam?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® Atrivim Serksis kamagh…®n Kwin Esta ko Judabar gumazim Mordekai m…®gei, ‚ÄúGua fo, Haman Judabagh as…®ghas…®ghasava amima, kamagh…®n k…® temem…®n aneguraz…®ma an areme. Ez…® k…® an biziba bar da isa Esta gan…®ngi.  
\v 8 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n guarara uan ifongiam…®n g…®n mang…® akatam osirigh uan adarazi Judaba, me bagh anemang…®s…® anemang. Gua ak…®nafarim osir…®va nan ziam…®n gavgavim ko nan ring…®n itir nedazim is…® ak…®nafarim…®n porogh, eght…® n…®n akaba gavgavim adar ikiam. Gumazamiziba bar fo, ak…®nafarir nan ring…®n nedazim itim, tav aneb…®ghan gavgaviba bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Mordekai atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazibav keme. Ez…® me ak…®nafariba osirigha da isa Judaba ko, gumazir dapanir ekiaba ko, nguibar ekiabar garir gumazir dapaniba ko, 127plan provinsbar garir gumazir ekiaba, provins…®n kaba da Indian provins…®n ikegha ghua Itiopian provins…®n tu, me me bagha vaghvagha da amada. Mordekai osirir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ia da osir…®va men nguibabar akabar me osirir arazim…®n akaba vaghvagh me bagh da osirigh, egh uaghan Judaba m…®geir akam…®n me bagh osirigh. Mordekai amir bizir kam, a iak…®nir namba 3 an ziam Sivan, an 23 aruem…®n oto.\f + \fr 8:9 \ft Judabar kalendan iak…®nir namba 3 Sivan, kar Pentikos…®n dughiam. Ez…® en iak…®nim…®n dughiar kam kar Mei ko Jun.\f* 
\v 10 Egha Mordekai atrivim…®n ziam…®n ak…®nafariba osirigha g…®vagha, atrivim…®n ring…®n nedazim…®n dar poke. Egha gumazir ak…®nafariba inigh mangamiba, me hoziar aghuir atrivim…®n ingangarimram amiba inigha, ak…®nafarir kaba inigha zuam…®ra nguibaba bar dar ghue. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® ak…®nafarir kabar osiziribar averiabar, atrivim…®n akar gavgavim dar iti. Da kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, nguibar an ativagha garibar aven, Judaba ko m…®soghs…® iz…® uari uari ak…®r…®va uari bagh gan, egh uarir akurvagham. Eght…® atrivim garir nguibabar dar m…®dorozir gumazir manaba, me iz…®va Judaba m…®soghs…® iz…®t…®, atrivim Judabar amamangat…®gham. Eght…® me uan ifongiam…®n gumaziba ko, amiziba ko, boriba ko m…®sogh me ag…®vagh men biziba bar ada iniam.  
\v 12 Egha Haman faragha Persian nguibar ekiam…®n akar kam ak…®ri, iak…®nir namba 12, an ziam Adar, an aruer 13…®n, a Judabagh as…®ghas…®ghasa dughiar kam at…®. Ez…® bizim ua ragh…®r…®, ez…® dughiar Haman at…®zir kamra, Judaba uan apanibav sogham.  
\v 13 Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam a atrivim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim an iti, egh bar mogh…®ra nguibabar mangam, eght…® gumazamiziba bar oregh fogham. Eght…® Judabar apaniba iz…®, me m…®soghamin dughiam, akar gavgavim uaghan men amamangat…®gha ghaze, Judaba uaghan men m…®dorozim ikarvagham.  
\v 14 Ez…® atrivim m…®geima gumazir ak…®nafariba inigha zuiba atrivim…®n hoziabagh apiagha ivemara bar zuam…®ra ghue. Egha me akar gavgavir kam bar Susan nguibar ekiam…®n aven uaghan anekuri. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® me Mordekai atrivim…®n korotiar ghurghurim ko blupla a garu. Egha inir p…®ghaghevir ruarir mam uaghan a garu. Egha g…®n atrivim…®n dapanir asuar aghuim a garu. A uab…® as…®ngigha atrivim…®n d…®penim ategha azenan zui. Ez…® Susan gumazamiziba an ganigha bar akuegha pamten diava arai.  
\v 16 Ez…® Judabar naviba deraz…®ma me am…®ragha iti. Me bar mogh…®ra bar akuegha fo, me uan apanim ab…®ragha g…®fa.  
\v 17 Ez…® nguibaba ko provinsba bar dar aven atrivim…®n akar gavgavim otoz…® Judaba bar a baraki. Egha Judaba bizir kam bagha, dughiar kam…®n isar ekiam gamigha avughsa ikia apa bar akuegha iti. Ez…® Judabar azenan itir gumazir av…®riba atiatigha iza men tong…®n ikia Judabar m…®n otiva Judabar arazibar g…®n zui. 
\c 9  
\s1 Judaba uan apanibagh as…®ghas…®ki 
\p  
\v 1 Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n, an aruer namba 13 oto. Dughiar kamra atrivim faragha akar gavgavim kamagh…®n anet…®gha ghaze, apaniba Judabagh as…®ghas…®gh me ab…®raghasa. Ez…® puvat…®, dughiar kam otoz…® Judaba ua ragh…®r…®gha me gas…®ghas…®gha me gafira.  
\v 2 Dughiar kam…®n atrivim garir provinsbar aven itir nguibaba, Judaba bar dar aven ikia uari akufa. Egha uan apanibar m…®doroziba ikarvaghasa uariv g…®a egha biziba ak…®ra iti. Ez…® atrivim garir nguibabar gumazamiziba bar Judabar atiatigha bizitam me damuan ibura.  
\v 3 Egha provinsba garir gumazir dapaniba ko, gumazir aruaba ko, gavman…®n gumazir dapaniba ko, atrivim…®n ingangaribar garir gumaziba, me bar Mordekain atiati. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bar Judabar akurvasi.  
\v 4 Kantrin kam…®n gumazamiziba bar fo, Mordekai dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven gavgavir ekiam atrivim…®n apengan a ini. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n an gavgavim ek…®va ghuavanagav…®ra iti.  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Judaba uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua uan apaniba puv…®ra me m…®suaghar…®si. Me m…®dorozir sababar suigha me ko uariv sogha me m…®sozi me ariaghiri. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Susan nguibar ekiamra me gumazir 500pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.  
\v 7-10 Judaba uaghan Haman…®n otarir 10pla bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Haman a Judabar apanim gamir gumazim, a Hamedatan otarim. An otaribar ziabar kara: Parsandata ko, Dalfon, Aspata, Porata, Adalia, Aridata, Parmasta, Arisai, Aridai ko, Vaisata. Me ariaghirez…®ma, Judaba men bizitam okemezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® dughiar kamra Susan nguibar ekiam…®n aven ariaghirezir gumazibar d…®bobonim…®n eghaghanim ghua atrivim bato.  
\v 12 Egha g…®n atrivim kamagh…®n Kwin Esta m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúSusan nguibamra Judaba gumazir 500pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® Haman…®n 10plan otariba uaghan ariaghire. Ez…® nguibar ekiar igharaziba e fozir puvat…®, ingangarim manmagh…®n ghuama!‚Äù 
\p Egha atrivim ua kamagh…®n Estan azara, ‚ÄúN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir tizim uam a gifonge? N…® ifongezir bizim bagh na m…®kemegh, eght…® k…® n…® danigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Esta atrivim ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan azangs…®zim gifuegh, egh a ikaragh. Egh Judan Susan itibar amamangat…®ght…® me dat…®r…®gh…®n amiz…® mogh…®n gurumzaraghan ua kamagh…®ra damu. Egh Haman…®n otarir ariaghirezibar kuaba inigh temer Haman asarazim…®n men f…®ribar afegh me aguigh.‚Äù  
\v 14 Ez…® atrivim me kamagh…®n damuasa a ifonge. Egha an akar kam Susan itir Judan gumaziba bagha anemada. Ez…® me dughiar kam…®n azenara gumazibar damazibar Haman…®n otaribar kuaba temem…®n me agui.  
\v 15 Ez…® Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n, an aruer namba 14…®n Judaba Susan nguibar ekiam…®n uari akufa. Egha 300plan gumaziba nguibar ekiam…®n me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Me ariaghirez…®ma Judaba men bizitaba okemezir puvat…®.  
\v 16 Ez…® atrivim garir provins…®n igharazibar itir Judaba, me uaghan uarira uari akuva derav…®ra ikiasa m…®gh…®gha m…®sosi. Me uan apaniba ko uariv sogha uan m…®doroziba ikarvasi. Egha gavgavigha m…®sogha egha 75,000plan gumazir men aghuazibav soghez…®ma me ariaghire. Ez…® me ariaghirez…®ma me men bizitam okemezir puvat…®.  
\v 17 Me Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n namba 13…®n aruem…®n, me apanibav soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® aruer namba 14…®n m…®dorozitam uam otozir puvat…®, ez…® Judaba dughiar kam…®n avughsa bar akuegha isar ekiam gami.  
\v 18 Ez…® Judan Susan nguibar ekiam…®n itiba, me Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n aruer namba 13 ko 14…®n uan apanibav sogha me ag…®va ghuav…®ra iti. Egha Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n namba 15…®n aruem…®n me avughsa bar akuegha isar ekiam gami.  
\v 19 Bizir kam bagha, Judan gumazamizir nguibar dozibar itiba bar bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha, Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n aruer 14…®n avughsa bar akuegha isar ekiam gamir dughiam. Me dughiar kam…®n uaghan uan bizir aghuiba uari ikarvagha uari gan…®di. 
\s1 Me Purim ar…®zir isar ekiam 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Mordekai bizir otivizir kaba bar ada osirigha g…®vagha, Persian nguibar Judaba itibar ada mang…®. Nguibar rogh…®ra itiba ko saghon itiba uaghara.  
\v 21 Egha a me m…®g…®a ghaze, Adar…®n iak…®nim…®n namba 14…®n aruem ko 15…®n aruem, kar ia zurara bar akuegh ikiamin dughiam.  
\v 22 Aruer kamning…®n Judaba uan apaniba ag…®fa. Ez…® iak…®nir kamra men os…®mt…®zim ko arareba g…®fa, ez…® Judabar naviba deraz…® me bar akonge. Ez…® Mordekai me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia isar ekiabav k…®m dar amu egh dar ik…®. Egh dagher aghuiba uari ikarvagh uari dan…®ng, egh gumazir biziba puvat…®ziba ia uaghan biziba me dan…®ng.  
\v 23 Ez…® Judaba Mordekai me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n azeniba vaghvagha me avughsa ikia isam gamuava apa, egha biziba uari ikarvagha uari gan…®dir arazir kam, a men arazir me zurara damuamim…®n m…®n oto. 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 9:24 \xt Esta 3:7\x*Me fo, fom…®ra Judabar apanim gamir gumazim Haman a Hamedatan otarim, egha Agak…®n adarazir mav. A Judabar apanim gamua, egh me m…®sueght…® me ar…®m…®ghirasa fofoghasa ikararer mam gamua egha dughiar mam bato. Ez…® Hibrun akam me fofoghasa ikararem gamim…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, dughiar kam ‚ÄúPurim,‚Äù a gar…®si. Dughiar kam, Haman Judaba bar me gas…®ghas…®ghasa a d…®boro. 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Esta atrivim bagha ghuz…® atrivim ak…®nafarir gavgavim osiri. Egha ghaze, ‚ÄúFom…®ra Haman Judaba bar me gas…®ghas…®ghasa akam at…®, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n os…®mt…®zir kamra uamategh iz…® a bativam.‚Äù Ez…® me temer an asarazimram aneguragha, uaghan an otariba gui.  
\v 26 Egha me bizir me bativizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n ami. Ez…® Mordekai ak…®nafarim amaga ghaze, me dughiar kam…®n avughsam. Ez…® kamagh…®n, me avughsazir dughiar kamning d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúPurim…®n Dughiar Ekiam.‚Äù Ez…® ziar kam Purim, an m…®ngarim kara, Satun Ikararem.  
\v 27 Ez…® Judaba dughiar kam gamiz…®ma, a me azenibar zurara damuamin arazim…®n m…®n iti, eght…® men ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba ko gumazamizir igharazir Judabar aven izamiba uaghan arazir kam…®n g…®n mangam. Egh azeniba bar, dar dughiar pumuning…®n Judaba Mordekai me m…®kemezir dughiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gham.  
\v 28 Egha me ghaze, Judan adarazir aven d…®peniba vaghvagh men ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba ko, gumazamizir provinsba bar dar itiba ko, nguibar bar ekiabar itiba bar, me Purim…®n dughiam g…®n…®ghn…®gh egh azeniba bar me avughsam. 
\p  
\v 29 Egha Abihail…®n guivim Kwin Esta, ko Mordekai, aning ak…®nafarir igharazir mam osiri. Ez…® Purim…®n Avughsamim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am an iti. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n Kwin Esta m…®g…®a, Mordekai faragha uab…®ra osirizir ak…®nafarim, gavgavim a gan…®di.  
\v 30 Egha aning Judan 127plan provins…®n Persian kantri aven itiba bagha ak…®nafarir kaba amangi. Ak…®nafariba kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúUa m…®doroziba puvat…®, ez…® ia bar guizbang…®ra naviba am…®ragh dabirabir aghuim…®n ik…®.  
\v 31 Egh ia uan ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba ko, ia Purim…®n Dughiar Ekiaba dar suighv…®ra ik…®. Mati ia faragha arava naviba os…®ava dagheba atagh…®razir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®. K…® Mordekai ko Kwin Esta, ga akar gavgavir kam bar mogh…®ra ia gan…®ngi.‚Äù  
\v 32 Ez…® Estan akar a Purim…®n Dughiar Ekiam bagha m…®kemezim gavgavim Purim gan…®di. Ez…® me ak…®nafarir mam…®n an osirigha anet…®z…®ma a iti. 
\c 10  
\s1 Atrivim Serksis ko Mordekai ziar ekiam iti 
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Atrivim Serksis ongarir dadarim…®n borogh…®n itir gumazamiziba ko, uan kantrin aven itir gumazamiziba inigha, me gamiz…®, me a garir nguazibar ingara iti.  
\v 2 Ez…® bizir ekiaba ko bizir aghuir atrivim amiziba ko, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar arazir a Mordekai gamiz…® a gumazir ekiam…®n otoziba, me bar da isa Persian atriviba ko Midian atrivibar ak…®nafaribar ada osiri.  
\v 3 Ez…® Judan gumazim Mordekai a uab…® atrivim…®n apengan ikia ingari, ez…® Atrivim Serksis uab…®ra an gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Ez…® Judaba bar a gifuegha an ziam fe. Ez…® a ingangarim gamima Judabar dabirabim bar dera. Kamagh…®ra, me atiatingan kogham. Eght…® men ovavir borir bar g…®n otivamiba men dabirabim deraghv…®ra ik…® mang…®v…®ra ikiam. 